verbose_text: Reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (PT-PCR) and western blot analysis were used to examine the expression of Toll interacting protein (Tollip), interleukin-1 receptor associated kinase 1 (IRAK1), Toll like receptor 4 (TLR4), nuclear factor-kappaB65 (NF-kappaB65) and TNF receptor associated factor 6 (TRAF6) in lung tissue.
evidence: expression of Toll-interacting protein (Tollip), interleukin-1 receptor-associated kinase 1
